quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  71,11,"He will shower you with abundant rain from the sky,",""
  71,12,"and He will give you wealth and children, and bestow upon you gardens and rivers.",""
  71,13,"What is the matter with you that you do not fear the Majesty of Allah<sup>3</sup>,","[3] While disobeying Him carelessly."
  71,14,"when He has created you in stages<sup>4</sup>?","[4] See 22:5 and 23:12-14 for the stages of the embryo."
  71,15,"Do you not see how Allah has created seven heavens, one above another,",""
  71,16,"and has placed the moon therein as a light and the sun as a burning lamp?",""
  71,17,"Allah has produced you from the earth like a plant<sup>5</sup>,","[5] i.e., your father Adam, whom Allah created from clay."
  71,18,"then He will return you into it and then will bring you out again.",""
  71,19,"Allah has made the earth widespread for you",""
  71,20,"so that you may tread its spacious paths<sup>6</sup>.’”","[6] In the pursuit of a lawful livelihood."
  71,21,"Noah said, “My Lord, they have disobeyed me and followed those whose wealth and children did not increase them except in loss<sup>7</sup>.","[7] i.e., the lowly people among them followed their wealthy chiefs."
  71,22,"They have contrived a mighty plot,",""
  71,23,"They said, ‘Do not abandon your gods; and do not abandon Wadd, Suwā‘, Yaghūth, Ya‘ūq, and Nasr<sup>8</sup>.’","[8] These were the names of idols named after pious men of past generations before the time of Noah, to commemorate them. In later generations, people started worshiping these idols."
  71,24,"They have led many astray. So [O Lord], do not increase the wrongdoers except in error.”",""
  71,25,"Because of their sins, they were drowned and then were cast into the Fire, and they did not find any helpers against Allah.",""
  71,26,"Noah said, “My Lord, do not leave on earth a single disbeliever.",""
  71,27,"For if You leave them, they will surely lead Your slaves astray and beget none but wicked disbelievers.",""
  71,28,"My Lord, forgive me and my parents, and whoever enters my house as a believer, and all the believing men and women, and do not increase the wrongdoers except in ruin.”",""
